<br>
The thing to watch out for is that those there for faction may try and tag every mob in sight rather than having the focus they need.<br>
<br>
Now, all that said, for folks that are in ANY way interested in raiding, a 10th ring war has to be one of the most exillerating events in the game. It's is quite the rush chasing mobs from the east, the west, the south, then back to the west again, etc., then watching that one giant that breaks ranks and rushes for the Thurg entrance. Most folks place a &quot;stopper&quot; group at the entrance that's sole purpose is to sit and wait (and perhaps rez and rebuff the occasionally dead drug back to them). In my two stints with it, I usuallyl took to midline fighting dotting from a distance but focusing on snaring any that broke ranks (to buy time) and calling in assistance or otherwise warning the stopper group. The mobs that make a break for it will often be very, very hard to gain aggro on as they become single minded to get to Thurg before you can kill them.<br>
<br>
Make sure, BTW, that you have someone with Atone/Memblur around the dwarves. Folks will regularly accidently aggro coldain due to a poorly chosen AoE or, quite often, just plain lag related issues. When this happens, mezz, memlur/atone. Folks should be instructed to stand and die otherwise. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=183.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=183.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=183.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=183.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.threadControl?topicID=183.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=183.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=183.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notifica